"- File OCR (F)\n"
"- CAPTCHA Solver (C)\n"
"- Audio Transcription (A)\n"
"- Smart Dictation (S)\n"
"- Announce Status (I)\n"
"- Label Object (L)\n"
"- Manage/Scan Labels (Shift+L)\n"
"- UI Explorer (E)\n"
